Invocation Name: cleaning blitz
des:
When the house is overwhelming don’t get bogged down by trying to do it all completely. Give yourself 1 hour to do what you can. Don’t know where to start. I will pick for you. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
